  <div xmlns:v="http://rdf.data-vocabulary.org/#" typeof="v:Review">
    <div class="main review-item" id="6815308">
        

  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/6815308/" class="title-link">读王小波的《未来世界》</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-6815308"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/96677509/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img1.doubanio.com/icon/user_normal.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/96677509/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">我是安安静静的</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2014-08-11"
      class="main-meta">2014-08-11 15:05:42</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_6815308_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                    王小波的《未来世界》起先有点像一部卓别林的黑白剧，虽然我印象中的卓别林的电影并不多，但大致上是相同的。基调是沉重的，沉重得没有声音，便用部分诙谐的内容穿插使整个故事进行下去。这里不得不提王小波原先是学数学的。本人不才，也甚是懒惰，因此每当他在文中提起什么...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/6815308/#comments">(2回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">5有用 / 0没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_6815308_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_6815308_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>

      
  



